================================================================================
Third-party trust anchors redistributed in verifier/trust-sources/
================================================================================

This repository vendors several PUBLIC certificate-authority root certificates,
used by the verifier to validate certificate and RFC 3161 timestamp chains. They
are redistributed verbatim for verification convenience, contain no private key
material, and remain the property of their respective owners. Their inclusion
here does not imply any endorsement by their issuers.

  * Google C2PA Root CA G3
    verifier/trust-sources/pixel/root.pem
    Sourced from the C2PA Conformance Programme / C2PA Trust List.

  * C2PA TSA Trust List
    verifier/trust-sources/c2pa-tsa/c2pa-tsa-trust-list.pem
    Redistributed from the C2PA Conformance Programme public trust list
    (https://github.com/c2pa-org/conformance-public).

  * DigiCert Trusted Root G4 and SSL.com Root Certification Authority RSA
    verifier/trust-sources/c2pa-tsa-fallback/fallback-tsa-roots.pem
    Public timestamping-authority roots, redistributed to anchor RFC 3161
    timestamp tokens emitted by those authorities.

The RealReel Root CA certificate (verifier/trust-sources/realreel/root.pem) is a
self-signed public root published by Whole Earth Labs LLC. The corresponding CA
private key is held in a hardware security module and is NOT part of this
repository.

================================================================================
Platform-attestation trust anchors embedded in ca/_shared/attestation/roots.ts
================================================================================

The CA's enrollment-time attestation validators embed several PUBLIC
certificate-authority roots as PEM strings, used to validate Apple App Attest
and Android Key Attestation chains. They contain no private key material and
remain the property of their respective owners.

  * Apple App Attestation Root CA
    Property of Apple Inc. Published at
    https://www.apple.com/certificateauthority/Apple_App_Attestation_Root_CA.pem

  * Google Hardware Attestation Roots
    Property of Google LLC. Extracted verbatim from the reference validation
    library github.com/google/android-key-attestation (Apache License 2.0).
    These are the self-signed roots at which real-device Android Key
    Attestation chains terminate.

